Localization.Name: Pico the Penguin Party Animal Green Plushie
Localization.Description: No one can shred the slopes or celebrate quite like Pico the Penguin. This version of the charming microTech mascot makes any occasion more fun and festive by sporting a vibrant green jacket and playful party hat.
